SplitThreader prep guide

Run CBS_LR to get segmented copy number data from a 


bedtools bamtobed $BAM > $BAM.bed

# Circular binary segmentation for long reads with a 1000 bp bin size (minimum segment length is 5X this bin size)
CBS-LR $BAM.bed 1000


Upload CBS-LR output (segmented_coverage.csv) and Sniffles output (variants.bedpe) to SplitThreader on the web





